Spring AI’s <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/blob/main/spring-ai-model/src/main/java/org/springframework/ai/chat/messages/Message.java">Message</a> interface facilitates multimodal AI models by introducing the <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/blob/main/spring-ai-commons/src/main/java/org/springframework/ai/content/Media.java">Media</a> type.
