<p>The <a href="https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/embeddings">Google GenAI Embeddings API</a> provides text embedding generation using Google&#8217;s embedding models through either the Gemini Developer API or Vertex AI.
This document describes how to create text embeddings using the Google GenAI Text embeddings API.</p>
